In-browser BibLaTeX database record generator.

Uses https://doi.org to retrieve standardized citation information and
transforms it into corresponding BibLaTeX database.

Acknowledgments

  - Uses Mithril.js for user interface
  - Uses Ghost animation from icons8.com
  - Uses reset.css to normalize browser behavior

Changes

  2022-07-15 Added support for 'pages' BibLaTeX entry.

